<h2><I>CGAL::Random_points_on_segment_2&lt;Point_2, Creator&gt;</I></h2>
<P>

<H3>Definition</H3>
<P>

The class <I><A HREF="Class_Random_points_on_segment_2.html#Cross_link_anchor_1704">Random_points_on_segment_2</A>&lt;<A HREF="../Kernel_23_ref/Class_Point_2.html#Cross_link_anchor_52">Point_2</A>, Creator&gt;</I> is an input iterator creating points uniformly
distributed on a segment. The default <I>Creator</I> is
<I><A HREF="../STL_Extension_ref/FunctionObjectClass_Creator_uniform_2.html#Cross_link_anchor_1566">Creator_uniform_2</A>&lt;<A HREF="../Kernel_23_ref/Class_Kernel_traits.html#Cross_link_anchor_28">Kernel_traits</A>&lt;P&gt;::<A HREF="../Kernel_23_ref/Concept_Kernel.html#Cross_link_anchor_0">Kernel</A>::RT,P&gt;</I>.
<P>

<H3>Is Model for the Concept</H3>InputIterator<BR>

<I><A HREF="Concept_PointGenerator.html#Cross_link_anchor_1680">PointGenerator</A></I>
<P>

<I>#include &lt;<A HREF="../../../include/CGAL/point_generators_2.h">CGAL/point_generators_2.h</A>&gt;</I>
<P>

